{"TopicId":216916,"ForumId":198,"TopicTitle":"Root Part Below an EnginePlate and Decoupler Causes Major Issues for a Craft","CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-28T01:57:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-28T01:57:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EKSP2 Version: \u003C/strong\u003E0.1.0.0.20892\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EKSP2 Version: \u003C/strong\u003E0.1.1.0.21572\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EKSP2 Version:\u003C/strong\u003E 0.1.2.0.22258\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating System:\u003C/strong\u003E Windows 10\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ECPU\u002BGPU\u002BRAM:\u003C/strong\u003E i9 9900K\u002B3070ti\u002B32GB\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EMods Used:\u003C/strong\u003E None\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E2 Videos for this Bug Report:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nFirst video shows it happening in space\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSecond video shows \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003ECOM\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E appears to be calculating between the two separated crafts soon after launch.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EFirst Video:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/-wr0cShyia4\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://youtu.be/-wr0cShyia4\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0(19 Seconds)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EThings of note:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLoss of control\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nCamera isn\u0027t focused on either craft\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAfter separation the throttle still affects both crafts\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nBoth crafts phase through each other\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSimilar result for 0.1.0.0 \u002B 0.1.1.0 \u002B 0.1.2.0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EHow to Replicate:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLoad supplied 0100RootPartSecondTank\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLoad 0100RootPartSecondTank again (Counters another bug)\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nGive a small amount of thrust to match the video\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nStage\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nPlay around with the throttle\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESave file from First Video:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/y1tk7wb0qaxq6b9/0100RootPartSecondTank.zip?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/y1tk7wb0qaxq6b9/0100RootPartSecondTank.zip?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ELog Files From First Video:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/3ddvvoqzcnbbxjz/Ksp2%20%2B%20Player%20Logs.zip?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/3ddvvoqzcnbbxjz/Ksp2%20%2B%20Player%20Logs.zip?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESecond Video:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/qxzK3KCqJtw\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://youtu.be/qxzK3KCqJtw\u003C/a\u003E (17 Seconds)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOne thing of Note:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nIt appears that in this case the Camera is focusing on the Center of Mass of both crafts\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ECraft File with Root Part on 2nd Tank From Second Video:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/pt06u8yyxyu7qv2/RootPart2ndTank.zip?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/pt06u8yyxyu7qv2/RootPart2ndTank.zip?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EWork Around:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nJettison the Engine Plate\u0027s fairing/shroud However \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E is not engaged anymore.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nChange root part to the top of the craft.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-06-01T04:26:19Z\u0022 title=\u002206/01/2023 04:26  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJune 1, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Anth12\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-28T03:07:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn addition:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeparating the decoupler from the engine stages does make things act differently.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-04-28T03:08:40Z\u0022 title=\u002204/28/2023 03:08  AM\u0022 data-short=